name: Shiny Dragons
description:
Written, performed, recorded and mixed by Robert Jarvis (Zeal) at The Pentagon.

My love and thanks to everyone who contributed their brains, limbs and vocal chords to this recording, and everyone who bought, stole, listened to, or broadcast anything Zeal in the past, present or future.

Mastered by William Bowden.

Cover art by Robert Jarvis.
